reviewText: Great gag gift.  I'm a dental hygienist and gave this to the other hygienist in the office.  I don't know if she's watched it yet, but it sure got a lot of laughs at our Christmas party!

The next time I buy a fetish video believe me I will make sure I check the run time. it is a little over 9 minutes. I thought it was a full length feature but it is not. No gags, no length, no fun and no good in my opinion. If there is more to it we who have purchased this thus far have been ripped off. I seriously want my money back.
